n and distribution pumps","Diesel exhaust fluid (DEF) tank","DEF heater","DEF sending unit","Diesel fuel injectors","Fuel rails","Fuel hard lines","Pressure regulator","Vacuum pump","High pressure oil pump","High pressure injection pump","Glow plugs","Glow plug harness","Glow plug controller","Pump mounted driver module","Diesel NOx sensor"]},{"name":"Seals & Gaskets","parts":["Crankshaft seal","Camshaft seals","Cylinder head gaskets","Oil pan gasket","Timing cover gasket","Valve cover gasket","Intake manifold gaskets","Valve guide seals","Transmission/transaxle seals","Transfer case seals","Differential seals"]},{"name":"Wear & Tear","parts":["Covered components within the powertrain system"]},{"name":"Roadside Assistance","parts":["Towing","Fuel delivery","Battery boost","Lockout services","Tire change with spare","Winching service"]}],"exclusions":["Axle seals","Freon and recharge","Batteries","ABS components (add-on available)","Vehicles over 4.5 tonnes","Farming/hauling, heavy construction work, principal off-road use, snowplow/emergency/police use"],"termsSections":[{"title":"$5,000 Per Claim Eligibility","content":"Vehicle models 10 years or newer and up to 200,000 km. $100 deductible. Unlimited KM plans: 12, 24 months. 36 months up to 90,000 km."},{"title":"$10,000 Per Claim Eligibility","content":"Vehicle models 8 years or newer and up to 160,000 km. $250 deductible. Unlimited KM: 12 months. 24 months/60,000 km. 36 months/90,000 km."},{"title":"Permitted Commercial Use","content":"Pick-up trucks, cargo vans (sprinter), delivery trucks, transport/sales/service vehicles, route work, light duty contracting (electrician, plumber, carpenter). Under 4.5 tonnes GVWR."},{"title":"GPS & Tech Package (Add-on)","content":"Back-up camera, digital display/GPS monitor, bluetooth/handsfree, GPS control module, keyless entry, touchscreen interface, parking assist, tire pressure monitoring, Wi-Fi/mobile data module."},{"title":"Car Rental","content":"Up to $40.00/day for co